The next one will be a commemorative issue, a compilation of our best pieces.
We are having a hard time deciding what will be included.

So you can see the beauty if you try!

She possesses little sister characteristics as well, just like you said.

Thighs that have yet to be tainted...
She is truly the ideal little sister!
To top it off, she looks stunning in glasses!
And these are not decorative glasses that are just for show.

You should not let those two bother you.
Mitsuki, why could not you come straight to our precious club meeting?

I have decided to join your club.
I look forward to working with you!
We need to take care of something important.
Kuriyama-san, Is this your first time visiting Hiromi's house?
Everyone around these parts has heard of the Nase family.
They have always owned a ton of land.
They also manage this area's Exterminators.
It would be wise to stay out of their way.
You are Nase Hiromi-san and Mitsuki-san, right?
I am Miroku Fujima from the Exterminator's Society.
It is nice to meet you!
I was staying here while I observed the Hollow Shadow.
You caught me on my way out.
I wanted to say goodbye to Izumi-san, but I am running short on time.
I have never seen someone from the Society before.
Until now, I had only heard rumors about them.
Anyone who tries to dig up information on the Society's leaders... gets killed!
In reality, they primarily manage identification for Exterminators.
They also single-handedly gather and compile data on Exterminators,
You can think of their office as a city hall for Exterminators.
Well, I shall be keeping this.
We broke the rules and went after the Hollow Shadow.
Do not hold it against her.
You should be grateful that she is only confiscating it for a month.
How will I pay my rent?
I-I could help you out a bit.
Is she in that dire of financial straits?
She always has a monstrous appetite as well.
I eat so much because my powers use my blood.
You do belong to a clan from a cursed bloodline.
I have something to say to you as well, Akihito-kun.
I cannot believe you intentionally went after the Hollow Shadow.
I was under the impression that you had a better understanding of yourself.
That is all I wanted to say.
Kuriyama-san, I would like to discuss your future, so please stick around for a bit.
Do not let it get you down!
If Izumi-san felt like it, she could have exiled you.
But she did not, so you can take it easy for now.
Well, I guess you could look at it that way.
Come on man, just back me up!
Are you working part-time again this year?
W-Well, I have not thought about it yet.
Could you introduce Kuriyama-san to your boss?
She might starve if you do not!
It is a simple job as a shop assistant.
But I get offers for one other job as well.
I always turn it down, but you could rake in the cash if you take it.
Have them tell you about it when we get there.
That is all I had to say.
He is a demon, so normal people cannot see him.
No, I did not mean to stare!
I was just thinking about how much you have changed.
Remember how you insisted that you did not
want to interact with others or join any clubs?
I did feel that way, but...
Some time ago, I had decided that I cannot interact with others,
and that I had no choice but to be alone, but...
I would not be so hasty.
It is not wise to suddenly convince yourself that you are not alone.
Akihito is a half-demon and nearly killed my brother.
Everyone knows precisely how dangerous Akihito can be,
so the Nase family observes and handles him as we see fit.
I am only keeping an eye on him.
Regardless, it is so much better than what I have known.
He is possessed by a demon.
Will not it consume that man if we leave him be?
I see you do not hesitate anymore.
Nothing will change if I am always lost and floundering.
I rushed over when I saw the Cage.
I have had my eye on that demon for quite some time.
My license is currently suspended anyway, so I could not do anything with it even if I kept it.
But that demon is worth at least fifty thousand yen.
I just cannot catch a break!
All I can do is whine on my blog!
That is why you are such an easy target for flamers.
I would feel bad if I did not give you something in return, so...
If you want a meal for adults, you got to have grilled meat!
That is not what I meant!
That is all you have to say?!
This is one of those moments that make you happy to be alive, is not it?
Oh, I guess Kuriyama-san has not heard about it yet.
It is a local festival that is held every year.
But it is pretty much a couples-only thing.
Single people probably would not have much fun there.
I am part of the Nase family.
But does not it look nice?
